data.description: Located between Northfield and Pigeon Falls sits this immaculate manufactured home w/att. two car garage, pole building, chicken coop and garden shed, all on almost one acre with country views.  This 1993 Marshfield Home has had the very best of care with updates such as newer flooring throughout, fresh paint, new roof '13 on house, new roof on garage in '21 and much more. The home has a split floor plan with a master bedroom and full bath on one end of the home and two more bedrooms and another full bath on the other end.  The two car att. garage is fully insulated w/power, installed air lines, concrete floor and water.  The property is .8 acres with views of the country, plenty of room for a garden and more. The chicken coop and 20x20 pole building both have power.  Very well cared for property that is absolutely move in ready!
